steps.name: Input search text and press Enter
$("app-search form input") set value("Global Tactics Producer (xte4z57mej5)")
Verify that the search result is correct
Verify that the service data is correct
$("app-service-widget/app-service-location") should have([text 'Russia', text 'Moscow', text '777 Hodkiewicz Radial, Delenaton, SC 59101-5929'])
$("app-service-widget") should have(text 'Ordering of this service will be approved automatically')
$("app-book/by text: Accept and continue") scroll into view(true)
$("app-book/by text: Accept and continue") get wrapped element()
$("app-time-step main div ion-button") should be([visible, 10 s.])
$("app-time-step div.footer ion-button") should not have([css class 'button-disabled', 10 s.])
$("app-time-step div.footer ion-button") should not be([visible, 10 s.])
$("app-confirmation-step div.footer ion-button") should not have([css class 'button-disabled', 10 s.])
$("app-confirmation-step div.footer ion-button") should not be([visible, 10 s.])
